title_bed_bats_review: Hotel in Cox's Bazar · 1 bedroom · 1 bed · 1 private bath
listing_description:
Hotel The Cox Today is a privately owned 5 Star Standard Luxury Hotel in Cox's Bazar, Bangladesh. It is situated in an attractive location of Kolatoli Road, Cox's Bazar which is only 5 minutes drive form the Cox's Bazar Airport. It is a place of choice of most of the newly married couples, and for those who prefer to stay in luxury with stunning view of The 'Bay of Bengal'.
Complimentary: buffet breakfast, swimming pool, gym and airport pick-up & drop service.
